{"tid":558631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與14歲女友赤裸牀上   被告認猥褻罪  只判感化","createTime":"2018-02-12T12:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T14:54:29.000Z","uid":136645,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1f54d8aeada542579db626e04db768e9ef53f438","tid":558631,"uid":136645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T12:17:28.000Z","msg":"女侍應與14歲女童相戀後，於去年7月在女童父母房間內對女童作猥褻行為。事主母親回家後，發現2人赤裸躺在牀上。女侍應早前承認「向年齡在16歲以下的兒童作出猥褻行為」罪，今在西九龍裁判法院被判處12月感化令。<br />\n<br />\n辯方引述受害人創傷報告指，23歲被告周頌晞所犯案件未對事主造成負面影響，事主情緒和生活亦無因此改變。感化官報告另指被告明白控罪嚴重，現已深感後悔，希望於本案結束後重過新生活。署理總裁判官蘇惠德接納2份報告內容，認同被告很大機會於案後過奉公守法的生活，遂判處感化令。<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：黃梓生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男女平等<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36256b86c36df7c567ed1ff80a76c87e7d34aae3","tid":558631,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T12:20:55.000Z","msg":"好平等呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6876fa0e68c9d6fd949acab19e6e76a4bb35c0","tid":558631,"uid":136662,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T12:21:49.000Z","msg":"磨豆腐感化令<br />\n入山洞坐幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3231b5a402d672de34905f715eb13155e4e69bb","tid":558631,"uid":90890,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T12:21:55.000Z","msg":"男嘅應該坐緊監俾人屌緊屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2562beb12f2db730189fdf725f303ce9160d19ba","tid":558631,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T12:22:09.000Z","msg":"磨豆腐"},{"pid":"a160943fb1fc0429e21263f94485d792439f7ebc","tid":558631,"uid":78622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2562beb12f2db730189fdf725f303ce9160d19ba","tid":558631,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T12:22:09.000Z","msg":"磨豆腐"},"citedBy":0,"rep